nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Mr Person1. Are you having any problems urinating? Burning, frequency, urgency? Any issues holding your urine or stool, difficulty walking, pain radiating up or down from your lower back on the sides? It would also be helpful if you could get your labs for Dr Person2 today so we can review the results.
